  "texts": [
    "IntroductionThere has been a significant uptick in interest in artificial intelligence (AI) applications and implications in recent years, attributed to AI's increasingly widespread use in education.",
    "Particularly noteworthy is the fact that ChatGPT, a generative conversational AI, has been at the forefront of this discourse, as multiple studies have demonstrated.",
    "Early proponents such as Adiguzel et al. [1] and Mogavi et al.",
    "[2] acknowledged the transformative potential of ally, ChatGPT's involvement in distinct areas of learning, such as programming [4] and teaching foreign languages [5], has expanded its role in the pedagogical sphere.",
    "These areas include teaching foreign languages and teaching programming."
  ]
}